---
import SkillsComponents from "./SkillsComponents.astro";
---

<section class="w-full h-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between mt-36 md:mt-56 lg:mt-48">
  <div id="item" class="w-full mb-12 md:mr-4">
    <h3 class="font-bold font-merriweather text-4xl text-white mb-3">About me</h3>
    <p class="font-work text-slate-400 text-xl leading-7 md:w-[500px]">
      I am a 
      <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">computer engineering student</span>, 
      self-taught web developer 
      <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">(i love frontend)</span> 
      and lover of the <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">JavaScript ecosystem</span>.
      Passionate about code, technology and development; adaptable and persevering, curious since I can remember and always looking for new things to learn. <br><br>
      I usually develop projects that are 
      <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">impactful and useful</span>, as well as 
      <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">small practice projects</span> 
      that help me to continue <span class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">increasing my coding skills</span>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div id="item" class="w-full text-left mt-8 md:mt-0">
    <h3 class="font-bold font-merriweather text-4xl text-white">Skills</h3>
    <SkillsComponents />
  </div>
</section>

